data.description: Welcome to your future home! This charming townhouse features 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and a spacious 1,392 sqft. With new LED lights, plush carpeting upstairs, and stylish laminate flooring downstairs. Conveniently located near shopping centers and Newport News Park, this isn't just a property. It's a haven waiting for you. Don't miss the chance to make this attractive townhouse your new home.
